data.description:
Come see this beautiful 5-bedroom | 2.5  bath home with upgrades galore! The home features 
a grand double door entrance, large dining room, and huge enclosed den. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, large island and stone countertops and is located right off the dining room. As you head upstairs, you'll see a large master bedroom with an upgraded bathroom including a large glass shower, huge tub and generous size walk in closet.  
The backyard is perfect for entertaining with a private pool, generous yard space and a covered patio that extends the full width of the home.
